15¤¤Changes to the regulations
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
Changes may be made to the regulations and price list with two
months' notice if the changes are not in your favour. Changes in
your favour may be made without prior notice. You will be notified
of any such changes in writing or electronically.
.br
You are obliged to notify &BANKNAVN. of any changes in your address or
email address. Any failure to do so that results in you not being
notified of changes will be your responsibility.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
In the event of changes to the regulations, these will be considered
accepted unless you inform &BANKNAVN. that you do not wish to be bound
by the new regulations, prior to the date on which they come into effect.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
If you inform the bank that you do not wish to be bound by the new
regulations, the agreement will be considered to have been terminated
as from the time at which the new regulations come into effect. If you
have paid a year's fee in advance, you will be reimbursed a
proportional amount of said fee.
