12.4¤¤Industrial action
:SKRSLUT.
.br
You cannot use your Visa/dankort card in Denmark if
&BANKNAVN. and/or the data
centres used by &BANKNAVN. become involved in industrial action. On the
commencement or termination of such a conflict, you will be informed of
same without undue delay through advertisements in the daily newspapers
and via other channels.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
You cannot expect to be able to use the card outside Denmark if one
or more of &BANKNAVN.'s data centres, and/or if one or more of
&BANKNAVN.'s international partners becomes involved in industrial
action. In the event of industrial action exclusively outside
Denmark, it will still be possible to use your Visa/dankort card
in Denmark.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
